## Git Commands

### Undo Last Commit (keep changes)
```bash
git reset --soft HEAD~1
```

### Discard All Local Changes
```bash
git checkout -- .
```

### Stash Changes
```bash
git stash
git stash pop
```

### View Recent Commits
```bash
git log --oneline -10
```

