## Next.js / Dev Server

### Clear Next.js Cache
```powershell
Remove-Item -Recurse -Force .next\cache -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue
```

### Full Clean Restart
```powershell
Get-Process node -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Stop-Process -Force
Remove-Item -Recurse -Force .next -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue
pnpm run dev
```

