## Troubleshooting

### "Port 3000 is in use"
```powershell
# Kill whatever is using port 3000
netstat -ano | findstr ":3000" | findstr "LISTENING"
# Note the PID (last column), then:
taskkill /PID <pid> /F
```

### Browser Not Showing Changes
1. Hard refresh: `Ctrl + Shift + R`
2. Clear Next.js cache: `Remove-Item -Recurse -Force .next\cache`
3. Restart dev server

### Cursor Browser Suppressing Dialogs
Native `window.confirm()` and `window.alert()` are suppressed by Cursor browser.
Use custom modal dialogs instead (see ContactDetailClient.tsx for example).
